ww.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/O70Shake-Courney-Love-feature-new-album-Petrichor-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/O70Shake-Courney-Love-feature-new-album-Petrichor-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/O70Shake-Courney-Love-feature-new-album-Petrichor-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/O70Shake-Courney-Love-feature-new-album-Petrichor-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/O70Shake-Courney-Love-feature-new-album-Petrichor-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/courtney-love">Courtney Love</a>将出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/070-shake">070 Shake</a>即将发行的新专辑《Petrichor》中。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/070-shake-modus-vivendi-review-2596241">070 Shake –“Modus Vivendi”评论：没有特色，说唱歌手的视野响亮而清晰</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据上个月公布的即将发行的唱片的曲目列表，这位独唱家和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hole">Hole</a>主唱将在名为“Song To The Siren”的合作中担任主角。</p><p> 《Petrichor》还将包含与 JT（《Into Your Garden》）和 Cam（《Never Let Us Fade》）的合作。</p><p>其他歌曲名称包括“Battlefield”、“Lungs”、“Blood On Your Hands”和“Love”。此外，070 Shake 的第三张全长唱片——2022 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/070-shake-announces-second-album-you-cant-kill-me-with-new-single-skin-and-bones-3211918">《You Can&#39;t Kill Me》</a>的后续作品——将收录这位美国说唱歌手/歌手最近的两部分单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/070-shake-announces-release-date-for-new-album-drops-music-video-with-lily-rose-depp-3803900">《Winter Baby / New Jersey Blues》</a> 。</p><p>该项目的完整曲目列表目前显示在<a href="https://music.apple.com/gb/album/petrichor/1770831839" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple Music</a>和<a href="https://open.spotify.com/prerelease/71gKmMevNGz5Tq1RaQdlWS?si=TG5wYN8XQOuuii0vIQLrRA&amp;go=1&amp;utm_campaign=fAfTD_96_fmly&amp;utm_source=Original_Original&amp;utm_medium=Original&amp;utm_content=0dbfc8b1-e08e-4bdb-9f6f-4fd38732cfc9_none_none_none_none_none_20241011_direct_def-jam-us_US_070Shake.lnk.to%2FPetrichor&amp;nd=1&amp;dlsi=22e730fce8fc4880" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Spotify</a>上 - 请查看下面的屏幕截图。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> JT、Courtney Love 和 Cam 出现在 070 Shake 的最新专辑 PETRICHOR 中。 <a href="https://t.co/zN4HYsTv56">pic.twitter.com/zN4HYsTv56</a></p><p> - 070 Shake 更新 (@070shakenews) <a href="https://twitter.com/070shakenews/status/1855284657207517536?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 11 月 9 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>去年，Love 选择了 070 Shake 的歌曲“The Pines”作为她为<a href="https://www.dazeddigital.com/music/article/60212/1/listen-courtney-love-exclusive-dame-vivienne-westwood-playlist" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Dazed</em></a>制作的派对播放列表。</p><h3> <strong>070 Shake 的“Petrichor”的完整曲目列表是：</strong></h3><p> <strong>1.“罪”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“大象”</strong><br /> <strong>3.《你的碎片》</strong><br /> <strong>4.《流浪汉》</strong><br /> <strong>5.“肺”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“进入你的花园”（壮举。JT）</strong><br /> <strong>7.《战场》</strong><br /> <strong>8.“冬季宝贝/新泽西蓝调”</strong><br /> <strong>9.《塞壬之歌》（070 Shake &amp; Courtney Love）</strong><br /> <strong>10.《我怎么了》</strong><br /> <strong>11.《你的手上有血》</strong><br /> <strong>12.“永不让我们褪色”（壮举。凸轮）</strong><br /> <strong>13.“爱”</strong></p><p> 《Petrichor》将于本周五（11 月 15 日）通过 Def Jam Recordings/GOOD Music 发行。<a href="https://070shake.lnk.to/Petrichor" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处预订/预先保存</a>。</p><p> 070 Shake（真名 Danielle Balbuena）与她的女友、演员、模特兼歌手莉莉-罗丝·德普 (Lily-Rose Depp) 一起出演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/070-shake-announces-release-date-for-new-album-drops-music-video-with-lily-rose-depp-3803900">“Winter Baby / New Jersey Blues”的官方音乐视频</a>。</p><p>今年 6 月，070 Shake 在接受<a href="https://www.culturedmag.com/article/2024/06/18/070-shake-musician-petrichor" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Cultured</em></a>采访时谈到《Petrichor》时解释道：“感觉就像呼吸了一口新鲜空气。 “Petrichor”是一种感觉，是描述这组音乐的完美词语。”</p><p>她对粉丝们继续说道：“我希望他们愿意接受它，并为此感到口渴和充满活力。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBJ0NOAyu4Q/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.1